                <h1>24X7 Medical Facilities<h1></h1>
                    <img src="/media/medical.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="rightside1">
                <p>Gandhi Engineering College has well equipped medical facility within the campus to provide first hand
                    emergency services to Faculty members and students. Serious cases are generally transferred to any
                    city hospital in Bhubaneswar. The institute provides 24 hours ambulance service.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

