            <div class="leftside3">
                <h1>Industry Visits & Study Tours<h1></h1>
                    <p>Experiential learning is one of the corner stone of the umbrella of modern pedagogies we employ
                        in our institution in order to keep our students abreast of latest technologies and know-hows
                        prevailing in the industries. Industry visit and study tour-both are organized keping in view
                        the abundance of opportunities students can avail during their live interactions with industry
                        experts and eminent research scholars of national and international reputed institutions. With
                        the change in environment and learning atmosphere, there comes an exponential spike in learning
                        behaviour and learning ability of the students.</p>

            </div>
